<section class="hero">
    <h1><em>Disciplined</em> Rebalancing</h1>
    <div class="hero-subtitle">Sell when bitcoin is high in its Power Law channel; rebuy when it's low. Inside a tax-advantaged wrapper, the friction goes away.</div>
    <p class="subtitle">When the Power Law channel becomes more than a model &mdash; when its bounded oscillations become triggers, and its asymmetric character becomes a discipline. Sell at percentile, rebuy at percentile, inside a wrapper that absorbs the friction. Two rules. Observable triggers.</p>
</section>

